Subject: [PATCH 0373/2351] Revert "drm/amd/display: enable DPG when disabling
 plane for phantom pipe"

This reverts commit d47d2f9392f69f069c31d60ac3088471b1e1c7d4.

regression detected by the change. Revert until
fix is available.

Signed-off-by: Qingqing Zhuo <qingqing.zhuo@amd.com>
